<D>__{they're madmen! they're heading for the prison level. if you hurry, you might catch them.}
<C>__{first officer}
<P>__{(to his troops)}
<D>__{follow me! you stand guard.}
<A>__{the troops hustle off down the hallway, leaving a guard to watch over the command office.}
<C>__{threepio}
